Package Bank

package Bank
  • Class
    Description
    Account
    Represents a bank account with features like deposit, withdraw, and transaction history.
    AccountType
    Enumeration defining the various types of bank accounts.
    CentralBank
    Represents a central bank that manages customers and their respective accounts.
    centralBankApp
    This class provides the main application for interacting with the central bank operations.
    CentralBankAppTest
    Test class for the CentralBankApp application.
    Customer
    Represents a customer in a banking system.
    Menu
    Represents a console-based menu for user interaction.
    Searchable
    Interface for retrieving customer and transaction details.
    Transactable
    Interface for financial transactions.
    TransactionLog
    Represents a record of a single transaction made on an account.
    TransactionType
    Enumerates the different types of financial transactions that can occur in the banking system.
